Package: teachr
Type: Package
Title: Extension to LearnR
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Michael Schneider
Maintainer: Michael Schneider <m.schneider.programmer@gmail.com>
Description: This package modifies LearnR's tutorial template to enable html 
    post/get requests to a provided server's URL. This allows a teacher to control
    how far into a tutorial students can progress and record student submissions 
    to coding exercises and quiz questions.
License: Apache License (>= 2.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
  learnr,
  shiny
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
URL: https://schneidercode.github.io/TeachR/
